{"word":"G2710 - καταχράομαι - katachráomai - kat-akh-rah'-om-ahee - Abuse","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">καταχράομαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">katachráomai</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">kat-akh-rah'-om-ahee</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Abuse</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - அனுபவி"},{"paragraph":"1. to use much or excessively or ill"},{"paragraph":"2. to use up, consume by use"},{"paragraph":"3. to use fully"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G2596 - κατά - katá - kat-ah'/2596\">G2596</a> and <a href=\"#/G5530 - χράομαι - chráomai - khrah'-om-ahee/5530\">G5530</a>; to <i>overuse</i>, that is, <i>misuse:</i> - abuse.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}